Name: Average time for Accepted + Wait - User across all process variants where it appears
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - User and the end of the case

Name: Total time spent in Accepted + Wait - User per case, aggregated by country
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and the end of case grouped by the last value of organization country

Name: Minimum time for Accepted + Wait - User in variants that also contain Completed + In Call
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - User and the end of the case

Name: Average time from Accepted + In Progress to Accepted + Wait - User
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - User'

Name: Total time between Accepted + Wait - User and the subsequent Completed + Resolved
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Average duration of Accepted + Wait - User compared to the duration of Accepted + Wait - Vendor in shared variants
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and the end of case where activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor occurs

Name: Average time from Accepted + Wait - User to Completed + In Call in variants where both activities occur
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - User and activity Completed + In Call for cases where activity Completed + In Call occurs

Name: Total elapsed time between the start of Accepted + Wait - User and the end of Completed + In Call when they appear in the same case
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Minimum cycle time of Accepted + Wait - User in variants that do not include Completed + In Call
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - User and the end of the case

Name: Average time for Accepted + Wait - User grouped by resource
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and the end of case grouped by the last value of org:resource

Name: Total time from Queued + Awaiting Assignment to Accepted + Wait - User in variants containing both
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Queued + Awaiting Assignment and activity Accepted + Wait - User for cases where activity Accepted + Wait - User occurs

Name: Average duration of Accepted + Wait - User relative to Accepted + Wait - Implementation within the same variant structures
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and the end of case where activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation occurs

Name: Time between the completion of Accepted + Wait - User and the next occurrence of Accepted + In Progress
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Total waiting time to Accepted + Wait - User after Accepted + Assigned
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - User'

Name: Average time it takes Accepted + Wait - User to be followed by Completed + Resolved in cases that never execute Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Elapsed time from case start to Accepted + Wait - User in variants that later include Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - User'

Name: Minimum time for Accepted + Wait - User in high-frequency variants (frequency > 100)
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - User and the end of the case

Name: Average cycle time of Accepted + Wait - User in variants where it directly precedes Completed + Resolved without intermediate activities
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Total time between consecutive occurrences of Accepted + Wait - User in the same case
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - User'

Name: Average duration of Accepted + Wait - User in cases originating from Brazil versus USA versus France
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and the end of case grouped by the last value of organization country
